Chitrahaar

Chitrahaar is an Android application that The app automatically plays videos of latest Hindi songs from Youtube. The app parses xml feed of live online hindi radio stations to recover song metadata and uses that to search and play corresponding videos from Youtube. No manual intervention is needed.

Download the app directly from Google play store at https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.aanchal.chitrahaar

To run the code, replace the value of DEVELOPER_KEY in DeveloperKey.java from null to your own key. The instructions for registering your application to obtain an Android API key are availabel at https://developers.google.com/youtube/android/player/register.

